<refnamediv><refname>imnormalize</refname><refpurpose>Normalize image values to a target range.</refpurpose></refnamediv>
<refsynopsisdiv><title>Syntax</title><synopsis>out = imnormalize(im)
out = imnormalize(im, alpha, beta)</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv>
<refsection><title>Description</title><para><function>imnormalize</function> scales each channel independently to <literal>[alpha, beta]</literal>.</para></refsection>
<refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting role="example"><![CDATA[
im = imread(fullpath(getIPCVpath() + "/images/" + "baboon.png"));
out = imnormalize(im);
]]></programlisting></refsection>
